<div class="box">
	<div class="header">
		<h3>Textile Quick Reference</h3>
	</div>
	<div class="body">
		<div class="two_columns">
			<div class="left_column half">
				<p>Block modifiers:<br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=header" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">Header: <strong>h<em>n</em>.</strong></a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=blockquote" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">Blockquote: <strong>bq.</strong></a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=footnote" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">Footnote: <strong>fn<em>n</em>.</strong></a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=numeric" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">Numeric list: <strong>#</strong></a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=bulleted" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">Bulleted list: <strong>*</strong></a><br /></p>
				<p class="res">Phrase modifiers:<br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=italic" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">_<em>emphasis</em>_</a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=bold" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">*<strong>strong</strong>*</a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=cite" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=500,height=300,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">??<cite>citation</cite>??</a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=delete" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=300,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">-deleted text-</a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=insert" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=300,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">+inserted text+</a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=super" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=300,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">^superscript^</a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=sub" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">~subscript~</a><br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=span" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">%span%</a><br /></p>
			</div>
			<div class="right_column half">
				<p>To apply attributes:<br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=attributes" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">(class)<br />(#id)<br />{style}<br />[language]</a><br /></p>
				<p>To align blocks:<br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=attributes" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=400,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">&#60; right<br />&#62; left<br />= center<br />&#60;&#62; justify</a><br /></p>
				<p>To insert a table:<br /> <a target="_blank" href="http://www.textpattern.com/help/?item=table" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'popupwindow', 'width=400,height=500,scrollbars,resizable'); return false;">|a|table|row|<br />|a|table|row|</a><br /></p>
			</div>
			<%= clear_both %>
		</div>
	</div>	
</div>